{"tid":2316240,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"倉鼠新手","createTime":"2020-12-07T17:36:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-29T20:22:24.000Z","uid":304247,"like":16,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"3fa93bfb86015f66b5056305a4b36e5ef2cb7d73","tid":2316240,"uid":304247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T17:36:14.000Z","msg":"繼上次我收養咗我學生隻倉鼠之後，個學生又買咗兩隻新倉鼠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一隻喺同我收養個隻一樣喺三線鼠，一隻喺黃金鼠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n次次我去補習都好心痛啲倉鼠。佢新買個隻三線鼠只係得一個好細嘅籠，連水樽都無。佢屋企人仲要無常識到將隻鼠成籠拎去曬太陽，嚇到我即刻擺翻隻鼠去陰涼地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢啲學生可以點教佢要尊重生命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n附我家傻仔老鼠圖一張<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rrZCV7u.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrrZCV7u.png&h=7a860b82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n隻傻仔老鼠成日爬籠，喺咪最好都係換個籠(唔想晒嘢)"},{"pid":"76ef2011d56a3a117e80577f9d7461cef5da55cf","tid":2316240,"uid":304247,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T17:37:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mMDDFAs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmMDDFAs.png&h=c4c3a253&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n爬籠圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97f066dafa880408f31b503ee14454cfec3a9fb7","tid":2316240,"uid":156326,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T17:40:18.000Z","msg":"教佢唔好養"},{"pid":"292629f081105e3df13cd80fb7f627d5dce4c744","tid":2316240,"uid":360961,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T17:45:59.000Z","msg":"有種膠嘅籠 係旺角I love Rabbit度有"},{"pid":"76fa8145b1a94b2616e0abe02aa341e7aaf287f8","tid":2316240,"uid":304247,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"97f066dafa880408f31b503ee14454cfec3a9fb7","tid":2316240,"uid":156326,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T17:40:18.000Z","msg":"教佢唔好養"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T17:47:38.000Z","msg":"佢會話:我買翻嚟嘅點解唔養得<br />\n佢只係當啲倉鼠喺佢嘅財產，想點都得<br />\n<br />\n我以為佢唔會再養先收養佢一開始買個隻倉鼠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e981e86b37b952e0e5e3b41f40efcd15134f8bf","tid":2316240,"uid":201414,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T18:20:10.000Z","msg":"聽過有人隻倉唔少心跳左油鍋 變左炸田鼠 千其唔好俾佢入廚房<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d92527e8ae721ce9f849612f07cff126b024deb2","tid":2316240,"uid":56865,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T18:29:32.000Z","msg":"換籠，留意2種鼠嘅空間需求不一樣<br />\n三線40cm up 黃金60 up<br />\n另外都可以上以下2個fb睇下post交流下<br />\n如果你養唔掂/冇咁多位，就免費開post俾人領養<br />\n<br />\n香港倉鼠交流團<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/thecutehamster/?ref=share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2Fthecutehamster%2F%3Fref%3Dshare&d=JQtp7%2BScZlazt5%2F0T0af7D632Ab34%2FJQlYP9Mjrnz38%3D&h=ac785587\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/thecutehamster/?ref=share</a><br />\n<br />\n香港倉鼠部落<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/520204165423202/?ref=share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F520204165423202%2F%3Fref%3Dshare&d=JQtp7%2BScZlazt5%2F0T0af7D632Ab34%2FJQlYP9Mjrnz38%3D&h=dfb46dba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/520204165423202/?ref=share</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你個學生睇嚟都係唔識養嫁啦，屋企人唔教就乜都冇用，下次你見一隻就放出去領養，有咁放早就咁早"},{"pid":"dab2d13300026de2c5f6eb43f85b4b733121b279","tid":2316240,"uid":351498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T19:25:49.000Z","msg":"比佢睇倉鼠食bb片<br />\n造成陰影<br />\n然後你幫佢養埋<br />\n<br />\n講到有幾毒得幾毒<br />\n咪撚比佢玩死動物"},{"pid":"995b42581ca94559882ed4d25a8a5a0c8a92e2aa","tid":2316240,"uid":377869,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T09:02:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84addfdba689697fc85c0ac18cb1510acbb89901","tid":2316240,"uid":101698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T15:05:59.000Z","msg":"好靚嘅毛，係銀狐？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3629d2ab4f3d99a8575686613a26d4c108a37863","tid":2316240,"uid":299372,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"76fa8145b1a94b2616e0abe02aa341e7aaf287f8","tid":2316240,"uid":304247,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"97f066dafa880408f31b503ee14454cfec3a9fb7","tid":2316240,"uid":156326,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T17:40:18.000Z","msg":"教佢唔好養"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T17:47:38.000Z","msg":"佢會話:我買翻嚟嘅點解唔養得<br />\n佢只係當啲倉鼠喺佢嘅財產，想點都得<br />\n<br />\n我以為佢唔會再養先收養佢一開始買個隻倉鼠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T15:12:29.000Z","msg":"唉,好恐怖<br />\n係咪支那人反代黎?"},{"pid":"fdb535fe337237e32c2c6e8011d1cd37b230ccde","tid":2316240,"uid":299372,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"995b42581ca94559882ed4d25a8a5a0c8a92e2aa","tid":2316240,"uid":377869,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T09:02:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T15:12:53.000Z","msg":"隻貓唔會搞鼠咩？"},{"pid":"79db4b55963c1ffd1c027f7a0c9eb708bb5191c6","tid":2316240,"uid":305994,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T15:16:46.000Z","msg":"倉鼠唔適合鐵籠 成日爬高爬低有危險性<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yMFOyz5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyMFOyz5.jpg&h=d3